media: ipu3-cio2: Rename CIO2_IMAGE_MAX_LENGTH as CIO2_IMAGE_MAX_HEIGHT

CIO2_IMAGE_MAX_LENGTH is the maximum height of the image. Rename it as
"CIO2_IMAGE_MAX_HEIGHT" in order to better describe what it is.

